title: Rent a great 2 bed / 2 bath! Plymouth Square is waiting for you!
posting_body: ['RENTAL INFO', 'Rental Rates:', '$1690/month', 'Location:', '15300 N 37th Ave Plymouth, MN 55446', 'Unit for Rent:', '2-BR 2-BA |', 'Square Feet:', '1003 sq ft |', 'Lease Length:', '12-Month', 'show contact info', 'PROPERTY AMENITIES', '➢ Bike Storage', '➢ Cardio Machines', '➢ Courtyard', '➢ Elevator', '➢ Free Weights', '➢ No Smoking', '➢ Recycling', '➢ Sauna', '➢ Spa/Hot Tub', '➢ Tennis Court', '➢ 24 Hour Availability', '➢ 24-Hour Fitness Center', '➢ 24-Hour Indoor Heated Pool', '➢ Barbecue/Grill Area', '➢ Controlled Access Building', '➢ Disposal Chutes', '➢ On-site Maintenance', '➢ On-site Management', '➢ Reservable Clubhouse', '➢ Volleyball Court', 'APARTMENT AMENITIES', '➢ Air Conditioning', '➢ Ceiling Fans', 'In Select Units', '➢ Dining Room', '➢ Fireplace In Select Units', '➢ Intercom/Call Box', '➢ Microwave', '➢ Patio/Balcony', '➢ Vaulted Ceiling In Select Units', '➢ Views', '➢ Walk-In Closets In Select Units', 'ADDITIONAL INFO', 'Description:', 'At Plymouth Square Apartment Homes, you have plenty of apartment options.', 'From our extensive amenity list to our convenient location outside Minneapolis, MN, we strive to exceed your expectations at every turn.', "Our apartment home floor plans range from one-bedroom units to spacious three-bedroom models for rent that provide all the space you'd need.", 'All apartments have a balcony and an in-unit washer/dryer.', 'We also offer off-street parking.', 'Our pet-friendly policy allows for up to two cats; however, our pet policy does not allow dogs.', 'Air conditioning and ceiling fans (in select units) will keep you cool during the warmer MN months, and select apartments have fireplaces for those cold winter nights.', 'Pet Policy:', 'Cats Allowed: 2 allowed, One time Fee $200.00, Rent $25.00, Deposit $200.00.', 'Pet 2: Non-refundable Fee $100, Deposit $100 and Rent $15', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Plymouth Square:', 'show contact info', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '4F2D5E24DF4B441']
